Enum Class SoundListEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SoundListEnum>
cz.cvut.copakond.sweetfluffysheep.model.utils.enums.SoundListEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<SoundListEnum>, Constable
public enum SoundListEnum extends Enum<SoundListEnum>
Enum representing a list of sound effects and music tracks used in the game.

Each enum constant contains information about the sound file name, whether it is a sound effect (SFX), whether it should play on repeat, the number of variants available, and the volume level.
